#1
avg_base_pay <- sfdata %>%
  group_by(JobTitle) %>%
  arrange(desc(BasePay, mean, na.rm = T))
## Warning: package 'bindrcpp' was built under R version 3.4.4
#Top 3 = Chief of Police, Chief, Fire Deparmtnet, and Gen Mgr, Public Trnsp Dept 
chief_police <- subset(sfdata, JobTitle == 'Chief of Police', select = c('JobTitle', 'BasePay'))
chief_fire <- subset(sfdata, JobTitle == 'Chief, Fire Department', select = c('JobTitle', 'BasePay'))
GM <- subset(sfdata, JobTitle == 'Gen Mgr, Public Trnsp Dept', select = c('JobTitle', 'BasePay'))

top_jobs <- rbind(chief_police, chief_fire, GM)
ggplot() + geom_histogram(data = top_jobs, aes(x = BasePay, color = JobTitle, fill = JobTitle), alpha = 1/2) +       
  geom_density(alpha = .3) + ggtitle('Top 3 Jobs of Highest Average Base Pay in SF') + xlab('Base Pay ($)') + 
  ylab('Count')

#2
levels(sfdata$Status) 
## [1] ""   "FT" "PT"
sfdata$Status[2:3]
## [1]  
## Levels:  FT PT
PT_Status <- subset(sfdata, Status == 'PT', select = c('Status', 'BasePay'))
FT_Status <- subset(sfdata, Status == 'FT', select = c('Status', 'BasePay'))
Status_1 <- rbind(PT_Status, FT_Status)
ggplot(data = Status_1, aes(Status, BasePay)) + geom_boxplot() + ggtitle('Base Pay by Status') + ylab("Base Pay ($)")

#3
year11 <- subset(sfdata, Year == '2011', select = c('Year', 'TotalPay', 'BasePay')) 
year12 <- subset(sfdata, Year == '2012', select = c('Year', 'TotalPay', 'BasePay')) 
year13 <- subset(sfdata, Year == '2013', select = c('Year', 'TotalPay', 'BasePay')) 
year14 <- subset(sfdata, Year == '2014', select = c('Year', 'TotalPay', 'BasePay')) 

all_years <- rbind(year11, year12, year13, year14)

ggplot(all_years, aes(BasePay, TotalPay, color = Year)) + geom_point() + facet_grid(.~Year) + geom_smooth(method = 'lm') + ggtitle('Total Pay versus Base Pay by Year') + xlab('Base Pay $') + ylab('Total Pay $')

#4
top_3 <- sfdata %>%
  group_by(JobTitle) %>%
  count(sort = TRUE)
realtop3<-top_3[1:3,]

transit_op <- subset(sfdata, JobTitle == "Transit Operator", select = c("JobTitle", "BasePay", "Year"))
special_nurse <- subset(sfdata, JobTitle == "Special Nurse", select = c("JobTitle", "BasePay", "Year"))
reg_nurse <- subset(sfdata, JobTitle == "Registered Nurse", select = c("JobTitle", "BasePay", "Year"))
  
finaldata <- rbind(transit_op, special_nurse, reg_nurse)

ggplot(finaldata, aes(x = as.factor(Year), y = BasePay, group = Year, fill = as.factor(Year))) + geom_boxplot()+
  facet_grid(.~JobTitle) + scale_fill_manual('Year', values = c("red", "blue", "green")) + ggtitle("Base Pay for   Top 3 Most Frequent Jobs") + xlab('Year') + ylab("Base Pay $")
